    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Wis 13, base attack bonus +2.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When attacking a target with a miss chance granted from a spell, sphere effect, supernatural or spell-like ability, you may take a penalty to your attack roll to reduce the miss chance for that attack. Each -1 penalty to the attack roll you take reduces the miss chance by 10%. You cannot use this feat to take a penalty greater than half of your base attack bonus (rounded up).</p>\n",
